      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was reading about some legal cases where churches are fighting govt rules. do u think religious orgs should be allowed to opt-out of govt mandates that go against their beliefs? or does that just end up undermining the secular nature of the state? which one is more important for a functional society?",
