    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if those opt-outs mean other people's rights are being ignored? like, if a religious group uses that exemption to deny service or access to others, isn't that just a way to bypass civil rights laws? doesn't that kind of undermine the whole point of a secular democracy where everyone is equal under the law?",
